BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:WAhqkMq0L1skD1kykQDN3
SUMMARY:Take one of 15 Historic Seattle Walking Tours Today!
DTSTAMP:20260301T153238Z
DTSTART:20260301T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Overview  Turbo charge your enthusiasm for WA History by 
	selecting one of 15 self-guided walks organized by Historic Seattle. Choic
	es include: Seattle Central Waterfront\, Pike Place Market Architecture\, 
	Pioneer Square\, Belltown\, Market to MOHAI\, and more! Each walk will tak
	e 1-2 hours\, depending on your group size\, stride length\, steps per min
	ute\, your luck at getting green crosswalk signals\, and how many coffee s
	tops you make along the way:-\\)  Not every walk is a loop\, so the tour m
	ay not end at or near the departure. A map and narrated tour makes it easy
	 to plan and follow.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/take
	-one-of-15-historic-seattle-walking-tours-today/18066386/2026-03-01T00\n\n
	From SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/take-one-of-15-historic-s
	eattle-walking-tours-today/18066386/2026-03-01T00
