	es include: Seattle Central Waterfront\, Pike Place Market Architecture\, 
	Pioneer Square\, Belltown\, Market to MOHAI\, and more! Each walk will tak
	e 1-2 hours\, depending on your group size\, stride length\, steps per min
	ute\, your luck at getting green crosswalk signals\, and how many coffee s
	tops you make along the way:-\\)  Not every walk is a loop\, so the tour m
	ay not end at or near the departure. A map and narrated tour makes it easy
