BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:5ZRRW8JVL2DIazIiYvVCB
SUMMARY:Cloud Room Coworking Open House Week
DTSTAMP:20260301T153239Z
DTSTART:20260303T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Curious about coworking and looking for the perfect spot to get
	 work done and reach your goals? Join us for a complimentary day during Op
	en House Week and experience what it’s like to be a part of our incredible
	 community!\n\nWhat's Included:\n\nFree Trial Day: Pick any day during Ope
	n House Week to try out our coworking space\, free of charge! Arrive anyti
	me 9am or later — whatever works best with your schedule.\n\nAccess to our
	 beautiful workspace including quiet desk space with monitors\, large loun
	ge area\, phone booths\, bar\, and outdoor patio.\n\nComplimentary coffee\
