DTSTART:20260303T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get a pizza slice and some great advice from Research Librarian
	s at the Lemieux Library! This is a great way to get ahead with your studi
	es and finish the quarter strong.\n\nResearch Librarians will be present t
	o help you.\n\nWe'll be working on things like: \n\nFinding research or po
	pular articles\n\nNarrowing your research topic\n\nSearching library datab
	ases \n\nCitations \n\nCome join us in LEML 369 \\(third floor of the Libr
	ary\, near the Circulation Desk\\)\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/
	#/details/slice-and-advice/17008240/2026-03-03T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Learn
	ing & Education
