	onnection. ✨ What to Expect: Inspiring keynote speakers and thought-provok
	ing panel discussions Networking opportunities with local leaders and indu
	stry trailblazers Evening Mixer & Fashion Show featuring local designers\,
	 heavy hors d'oeuvres\, and drinks A dynamic Women's Empowerment Breakfast
	 \\(breakfast included\\) Exclusive vendor market showcasing women-owned b
	usinesses Presentation of the Impactful Woman of Kent \\(IWOK\\) Award  Sp
	onsorship Opportunities Whether you're an established professional or just
	 beginning your leadership journey\, The Era of Her is your space to grow\
	, connect\, and celebrate the power of women in our community.  Interested
	 in Speaking at out 2026 Women&'s Conference?  Click this link to fill our
	 our interest form!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/women
