DESCRIPTION:Curious about coworking and looking for the perfect spot to get
	 work done and reach your goals? Join us for a complimentary day during ou
	r upcoming Open House Week and experience what it's like to be a part of o
	ur incredible community! What's Included: One Free Trial Day: Pick any day
	 during Open House Week to try out our coworking space\, free of charge! A
	rrive anytime 9am or later - whatever works best with your schedule. Acces
	s to our beautiful workspace including quiet desk space with monitors\, la
	rge lounge area\, phone booths\, bar\, and outdoor patio. Complimentary co
	ffee\, tea\, snacks and kombucha. High-speed Wi-Fi\, printing\, and meetin
	g rooms available for rent The chance to meet like-minded professionals an
	d get a feel for the Cloud Room vibe. Special Offer: If you love your free
	 day with us and decide to become a member\, we'll waive your initiation f
	ees when you sign up! How to Join: Reserve your free trial day by selectin
	g one day of your choice on our Calendly \\(one free trial day per person\
	\) Show up and enjoy your day at Cloud Room! Be sure to check in with the 
	staff at the front of the lounge so we can give you a quick tour of the sp
	ace and get you set up with the wifi. Sign up for membership to take advan
	tage of waived initiation fees. Don't miss this chance to test out our spa
	ce\, meet amazing people\, and see if Cloud Room is the perfect fit for yo
	ur work needs! Current Promotions: ⭐️ Sign up for a grounded membership and
	 get your first month free \\+ 10% off you first year of membership. 3 mon
	th commitment required. ⭐️ Q1 Kickstart: Take 50% off your first full month
	 of membership when you sign on before March 31st\, 2026. Spaces are limit
	ed- RSVP here today.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/clou
	d-room-coworking-open-house-week/18050488/2026-03-06T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday -
