UID:NzAsOtd9Bkgy9IhCTofXP
SUMMARY:CL 101: Intro to Concert Lighting
DTSTAMP:20260301T153239Z
DTSTART:20260307T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:In this 2-hour workshop\, students will have a practical grasp 
	on lighting concepts and console operation\, learn about different lightin
	g instruments\, and gain hands-on experience programming lights for Vera’s
	 mainstage. Participants of the class will also gain basic fundamental kno
	wledge of working with artists and production staff to elevate the concert
	 experience as a lighting engineer. Complete this class to be eligible for
	 Lighting Engineer volunteer shifts at Vera shows. Become a volunteer at V
	era to access other production-related opportunities!\n\nhttps://seatoday.
	6amcity.com/events/#/details/cl-101-intro-to-concert-lighting/17683013/202
