	 of sailing. Topics will include terminology for parts of the boat and poi
	nts of sail\, as well as the basic theory of sailing. With the class you w
	ill receive the CWB Sailing Primer! Shore School can be taken independentl
	y or as part of the SailNOW! or US Sailing Basic Keelboat Certification co
	urses.\n\nMore information here\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/d
