SUMMARY:Open Adoption Hours
DTSTAMP:20260301T153240Z
DTSTART:20260310T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Audience: Adults\,Family\,Pets\,Senior\n\nWebsite: https://w ww
	.seattle.gov/animal-shelter/find-an-animal/adopt\n\nNeighborhoods: Citywid
